hor.</p> <p class=\"peCaption\">Each page must have some text.</p> <p class=\"peCaptionLength\">The text on each page must be less than 130 characters in length.</p> <p class=\"peLength\">It must have at least 3 pages.</p> <p class=\"peLanguage\">It must specify the language.</p> <p class=\"peCategories\">It must be in no more than 4 categories.</p> <p class=\"pePermission\">You must check that you have permission to use uploaded images.</p> <p class=\"peSaved\">Your book has been saved as a draft.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div></div><div style=\"display:none\" class=\"writeLabels\"> <span class=\"wlAddToBook\">Add to Book</span> <span class=\"wlClose\">Close</span> <span class=\"wlPrevious\">Previous</span> <span class=\"wlNext\">Next</span> <span class=\"wlPageAdded\">Page added to your book</span> <span class=\"wlPageCopied\">Page duplicated</span> <div class=\"wEditHelp\"> <img class=\"help\" src=\"images/help.png\" title=\"Click for help\" alt=\"Click for help\"/> <p class=\"help-text\" title=\"Page Editor Help\">Click on the text to change it. You may use the next and previous buttons to move between pages. When you're finished, close the editor by clicking on the x in the upper right.</p> </div> <span class=\"wlClickToEdit\">Click to edit</span> <span class=\"wDeleteThisPage\">Delete this page</span> <span class=\"wCopyThisPage\">Duplicate this page</span> <span class=\"wLoseWork\">If you leave you will lose your work on this book.</span> <div class=\"wUploader\" ><div class=\"qq-uploader\" ><div class=\"qq-upload-drop-area\"><span>Drop files here to upload</span></div ><div class=\"qq-upload-button\">Upload</div ><ul class=\"qq-upload-list\"></ul ></div ></div> <div class=\"wUploaderLi\" ><li ><span class=\"qq-upload-file\"></span ><span class=\"qq-upload-spinner\"></span ><span class=\"qq-upload-size\"></span ><a class=\"qq-upload-cancel\" href=\"#\">Cancel</a ><span class=\"qq-upload-failed-text\">Failed</span ></li ></div></div>","yourbooks":"<noscript><